港 時代革命</span><br />\n</div></strong>"},{"pid":"89bc0e5c9c82087cb85b693a4d2e6234dda0fb56","tid":1453860,"uid":40649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"起新壇你認為有幫助？<br />\n新壇一樣可以有三毛<br />\n連仔已經做左好多野<br />\n請支持LIHKG"},{"pid":"77230c4b05136e278bcffb5ec9be7288e98309b9","tid":1453860,"uid":147721,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:49.000Z","msg":"新壇=幾乎全部都係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243280c08fce0d6e475858a8c9d5d02e1c7db24b","tid":1453860,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"6月前已經有大把打手啦<br />\n係你地成日要冇大台，俾人撚狗"},{"pid":"5a62f544bd007efb44e48f862ae2e9032f4b47f2","tid":1453860,"uid":56546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"連仔再唔禁新會員開post<br />\n<br />\n好快變舊登"},{"pid":"8f1ddd3e9ab12c776157247e395abc35c6292207","tid":1453860,"uid":78085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a62f544bd007efb44e48f862ae2e9032f4b47f2","tid":1453860,"uid":56546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"連仔再唔禁新會員開post<br />\n<br />\n好快變舊登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"真!"},{"pid":"faca525002a6ccf8fdd36a2bfb38602cd79dad9f","tid":1453860,"uid":78085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89bc0e5c9c82087cb85b693a4d2e6234dda0fb56","tid":1453860,"uid":40649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"起新壇你認為有幫助？<br />\n新壇一樣可以有三毛<br />\n連仔已經做左好多野<br />\n請支持LIHKG"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">200%支持連仔 但新會員一定要禁</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b18d20cb816c6777385bfb21a0fe73ca073e373","tid":1453860,"uid":23726